---
// About Section
---

<section id="nosotros" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Sobre SolarPay SV</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Somos pioneros en El Salvador en hacer la energía solar accesible para todos mediante 
          soluciones de financiamiento flexibles.
        </p>
        <p>
          Desde 2024, hemos ayudado a más de 100 familias y negocios a reducir sus costos 
          energéticos y contribuir al cuidado del medio ambiente. Nuestro equipo de expertos 
          certificados se encarga de todo el proceso: desde el diseño personalizado hasta la 
          instalación y mantenimiento continuo.
        </p>
        <div class="about-features">
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Instaladores Certificados</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Equipos de Primera Calidad</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Garantía Extendida</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Soporte 24/7</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn-cta">Solicita tu cotización gratuita</a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <div class="solar-icon">☀️</div>
          <div class="stats-overlay">
            <div class="overlay-stat">
              <strong>100+</strong>
              <span>Instalaciones</span>
            </div>
            <div class="overlay-stat">
              <strong>100%</strong>
              <span>Satisfacción</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #ea580c 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5);
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #ea580c 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .solar-icon {
    font-size: 8rem;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .stats-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 2rem;
    right: 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .overlay-stat {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .overlay-stat strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .overlay-stat span {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      height: 350px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
